org.bytedeco.javacpp

Class avformat.AVIODirEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.javacpp.avformat.AVIODirEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Enclosing class:
    avformat

    public static class avformat.AVIODirEntry
extends Pointer
    Describes single entry of the directory. Only name and type fields are guaranteed be set. Rest of fields are protocol or/and platform dependent and might be unknown.
